{"tid":755692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解醫學/科學上仲堅持用拉丁文?","createTime":"2018-07-25T11:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T17:11:09.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a2761a0d09ec68ac68eba03b47eb0fdbe539224b","tid":755692,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"1.其實用英文闡釋唔到咩? 點解仲要記多咁多生字?<br />\n<br />\n2.英文學名起碼一般人可能可以睇字都估到<br />\n但係行外人識拉丁文係少之又少<br />\n<br />\n真心膠求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e5a19fe98fe009c03db3752810f9362e10cbaf","tid":755692,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"以前讀biochem基本上冇拉丁文 好似alcohol dehydrogenase咁<br />\n做咩就叫咩<br />\n醫學撚都少用拉丁文 除非係以前叫落既組織/部位名"},{"pid":"25c5bfb4e47a6e7f515c69ed25042306073b87dd","tid":755692,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"a.a.a m.d.u t.d.s q6h"},{"pid":"6d04c680eb4b410f670d93aa565d20edb07ebe8a","tid":755692,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"以前定落的習慣？<br />\n如果要改的話<br />\n可能有段長時間會出現溝通問題<br />\n老一輩就講拉丁文 年輕的就講英文<br />\n以前的書籍 論文會變成文言文咁冇人識睇"},{"pid":"42c999265e96f25f4dc4b3d5d7ef0b5ebff58d11","tid":755692,"uid":179547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"提高門檻"},{"pid":"6034c1f94608155934d7951fb105779cbddc9eb4","tid":755692,"uid":125479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"未又係字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時未又係了解隻字後面個意思"},{"pid":"17e2d38f8436cadd881fee121ce900f58629846a","tid":755692,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"試下咁諗, 起羅馬人希臘人眼中, 佢地見到你地用拉丁文古希臘文就覺得好簡單好親切<br />\n反而你用英文, 佢地見到就好似我地見到拉丁文古希臘文咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利