唔同情況有好多conjugations 所以係非常難學同難係日常使用既語言<br />\n<br />\n但係係醫學科學上係要求非常精準既定義同解釋 而且全世界都用拉丁文(詞)做定義 所以用拉丁文可以減少誤會同一定可以表達你想要既解釋或者key words"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"即係比英文準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"拉丁文係有好多conjugations<br />\n但係現代嘅醫學上都只係借咗啲字嚟用<br />\n但係grammar都係跟返英文(or 你使用嘅語言)<br />\n所以其實真係只係傳統問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"我以為佢借左既字已經係conjugate左 所以已經加左你想形容既野落去<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"8dea73a8a36be338e5a3c345892872efcafb6219","tid":755692,"uid":33213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d8d34d602410cb6855a26ed20b3f4506450e404","tid":755692,"uid":126838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f85d7c0cbfa5cbd8f809909779ac21bbd4fa81f0","tid":755692,"uid":33213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b3a498f4daa0c3af619233144ef45b836e4f006","tid":755692,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"即係比英文準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"拉丁文係有好多conjugations<br />\n但係現代嘅醫學上都只係借咗啲字嚟用<br />\n但係grammar都係跟返英文(or 你使用嘅語言)<br />\n所以其實真係只係傳統問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"我以為佢借左既字已經係conjugate左 所以已經加左你想形容既野落去<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"英文喺拉丁文主要係借咗啲 derivational affixes 同埋 root<br />\n例如話 renal 咁<br />\nren- 就真係由拉丁文照搬過嚟，解腎<br />\n-al 嘅終極來源係拉丁文 -alis ，係一個名詞轉形容詞嘅suffix，但係個樣已經唔同咗<br />\n主流意見係認為英文唔係直接抄拉丁文，而係抄咗中古法文<br />\n<br />\n但係 -al 呢個suffix喺其他字都成日見，好似話 origin-al, norm-al咁，可以話佢已經融入咗英文嘅 grammar入面，所以仲係唔係呢個post所講嘅「堅持用拉丁文」實在有待商榷<br />\n<br />\n而你講到嘅conjugation就係用係表達 grammatical 嘅意思，例如noun會分 singular/plural，person (1st/2nd/3rd)，case (喺句子入面嘅功能，好似話subject/object咁)<br />\n而呢類grammar係唔可能搬到其他語言嘅<br />\n唔係嘅話你見到嘅就唔係renal<br />\n而係 renalis, renali, renalium, renalibus, renales, etc."},{"pid":"3452922aae0f716abc9f30ec73fc8c6e60520ea3","tid":755692,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"現代最早教anatomy既大學係意大利既博洛尼亞，文藝復興個時學術界既官方語言仍然係拉丁文，其次就係古希臘文（例如anatomē就係希臘文），之後去歐洲其他地方教學既教授都係受拉丁文教育，所以醫學用詞都係來自呢兩大語種"},{"pid":"2bcdddfe6600dee7331238a6b9db3397e910f142","tid":755692,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b13845279224af97e25b84b4951c00f32abb89fb","tid":755692,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"因為唔係人人用英文<br />\n<br />\nWiki:-<br />\n<br />\nVulgar Latin developed into the Romance languages, such as Italian, <ins>Portuguese, Spanish, French</ins>, and Romanian."},{"pid":"1c805503f0e14fe3fd911efffbea2de435357e2f","tid":755692,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bcdddfe6600dee7331238a6b9db3397e910f142","tid":755692,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dea73a8a36be338e5a3c345892872efcafb6219","tid":755692,"uid":33213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d8d34d602410cb6855a26ed20b3f4506450e404","tid":755692,"uid":126838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"我以為佢借左既字已經係conjugate左 所以已經加左你想形容既野落去<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"英文喺拉丁文主要係借咗啲 derivational affixes 同埋 root<br />\n例如話 renal 咁<br />\nren- 就真係由拉丁文照搬過嚟，解腎<br />\n-al 嘅終極來源係拉丁文 -alis ，係一個名詞轉形容詞嘅suffix，但係個樣已經唔同咗<br />\n主流意見係認為英文唔係直接抄拉丁文，而係抄咗中古法文<br />\n<br />\n但係 -al 呢個suffix喺其他字都成日見，好似話 origin-al, norm-al咁，可以話佢已經融入咗英文嘅 grammar入面，所以仲係唔係呢個post所講嘅「堅持用拉丁文」實在有待商榷<br />\n<br />\n而你講到嘅conjugation就係用係表達 grammatical 嘅意思，例如noun會分 singular/plural，person (1st/2nd/3rd)，case (喺句子入面嘅功能，好似話subject/object咁)<br />\n而呢類grammar係唔可能搬到其他語言嘅<br />\n唔係嘅話你見到嘅就唔係renal<br />\n而係 renalis, renali, renalium, renalibus, renales, etc."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e113a91fcf3e69464900ec2717c58487f9dec3","tid":755692,"uid":179120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"其實好多英文都係來自拉丁文，所以唔係完全冇關連<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe3fe91ec2504c6bbf02b8a881c9611687e7bf0","tid":755692,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfad225db1b85ef83911a253c254999a9edde44b","tid":755692,"uid":179120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fe3fe91ec2504c6bbf02b8a881c9611687e7bf0","tid":755692,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e113a91fcf3e69464900ec2717c58487f9dec3","tid":755692,"uid":179120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"其實好多英文都係來自拉丁文，所以唔係完全冇關連<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.infoplease.com/arts-entertainment/writing-and-language/latin-roots-prefixes-and-suffixes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infoplease.com%2Farts-entertainment%2Fwriting-and-language%2Flatin-roots-prefixes-and-suffixes&d=91oCUQQWuPg22LfIbv5bvdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a30a8c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infoplease.com/arts-entertainment/writing-and-language/latin-roots-prefixes-and-suffixes</a>"}]}